# Header Options -------------------------------------
ignore *
unignore from: to: cc: date: List-Unsubscribe: X-GitHub-Reason: subject: # show only these
unhdr_order *
hdr_order from: to: cc: date: List-Unsubscribe: X-GitHub-Reason: subject: # and in this order

